select store_nbr,region_en,city_cn,vendor_nbr,vendor_name,category_nbr,sub_category_nbr,upc,old_nbr,primary_desc,po_nbr,order_date,sams_po_type,net_vnpk_cost,whpk_cost,whpk_qty,po_status_desc,event_desc,ship_date,cancel_date,buyer_name,
whpk_order_qty,whpk_rec_qty,whpk_order_qty-whpk_rec_qty as diff 
from 
(select store_nbr,region_en,city_cn,vendor_nbr,vendor_name,category_nbr,sub_category_nbr,upc,old_nbr,primary_desc,po_nbr,order_date,sams_po_type,net_vnpk_cost,whpk_cost,whpk_qty,po_status_desc,event_desc,ship_date,cancel_date,buyer_name,
sum(whpk_ordered_qty) as whpk_order_qty,sum(whpk_received_qty) as whpk_rec_qty
from 
(select t4.store_nbr,t4.region_en,t4.city_cn,t5.category_nbr,t5.sub_category_nbr,t5.vendor_nbr,t5.vendor_name,t5.old_nbr,t5.upc,t5.primary_desc,t4.order_date,t4.po_nbr,t4.sams_po_type,
t4.line_nbr,t4.net_vnpk_cost,t4.whpk_cost,t5.whpk_qty,t4.whpk_ordered_qty,t4.whpk_received_qty,t4.po_status,t6.po_status_desc,t4.discount_desc,
t4.event_desc,t4.ship_date,t4.cancel_date,t4.buyer_name,t4.wm_week_nbr,t4.last_chg_date,t4.total_cost,t4.total_retail,t4.pay_discount_desc 
from 
(select t1.store_nbr,t1.region_en,t1.city_cn,t2.item_nbr,t2.order_date,t1.po_nbr,t3.sams_po_type,t1.line_nbr,t2.net_vnpk_cost,t2.whpk_cost,t1.whpk_ordered_qty,t1.whpk_received_qty,t3.po_status,t3.discount_desc,
t3.event_desc,t3.ship_date,t3.cancel_date,t3.buyer_name,t3.wm_week_nbr,t3.last_chg_date,t3.total_cost,t3.total_retail,t3.pay_discount_desc 
from
(select s1.po_nbr,s1.line_nbr,s1.store_nbr,s1.whpk_ordered_qty,s1.whpk_received_qty,s2.region_en,s2.city_cn
from 
(select po_nbr,line_nbr,store_nbr,whpk_ordered_qty,whpk_received_qty from ods.cn_wc_vm__po_line_distribution_d where ts>=date_sub(current_date(),60) 
)s1 
inner join 
(select store_id,region_en,go_date,province_cn,city_cn from ods.storecenter__store_main_info where store_type='Sams' and ((store_status<>0 and store_status<>8) or store_name_full regexp '拣货|DC')  --山姆店号
)s2 on s1.store_nbr=s2.store_id
)t1
inner join 
(select po_nbr,line_nbr,item_nbr,order_date,net_vnpk_cost,whpk_cost from ods.cn_wc_vm__po_line_d where ts>=date_sub(current_date(),60) 
)t2 on t1.po_nbr=t2.po_nbr and t1.line_nbr=t2.line_nbr 
inner join 
(select po_nbr,po_status,sams_po_type,discount_desc,event_desc,ship_date,cancel_date,buyer_name,wm_week_nbr,last_chg_date,total_cost,total_retail,pay_discount_desc 
from ods.cn_wc_vm__purchase_order_d where ts>=date_sub(current_date(),60) 
)t3 on t2.po_nbr=t3.po_nbr
)t4
left join ods.cn_wc_vm__item_desc_ascii t5 on t4.item_nbr=t5.item_nbr
left join ods.cn_wc_vm__po_status_txt t6 on t4.po_status=t6.po_status_code
)a 
group by store_nbr,region_en,city_cn,vendor_nbr,vendor_name,category_nbr,sub_category_nbr,upc,old_nbr,primary_desc,po_nbr,order_date,sams_po_type,net_vnpk_cost,whpk_cost,whpk_qty,po_status_desc,event_desc,ship_date,cancel_date,buyer_name
)aa 
where event_desc not like '%OPEN%' 
or whpk_rec_qty > 1.15 * whpk_order_qty
